name: Color is Everything
description:
Colored trays are now avaliable in yellow , pink,  purple, blue and orange. We offer these colors at the same price as the pure white.
Add these as storage trays in your bedroom , closet, bathroom, garage, office or shop. The trays are perfect for tailgate parties. Organize with color being your design.

name: Cabinet Keeper Tray (QTY 1)
description:
The Cabinet Keeper tray design is a 18 x 16.5 inch multi-purpose, high impact rigid plastic interlocking tray. The tray is a storage and organization product that can be used for protecting cabinets or storage areas from damage resulting from moisture or leaks. The tray provides an easy to use method to organize any area of the home, office, business, boat or RV.  The Cabinet Keeper is made in the USA from high quality materials built to be durable for years.
Thank you for your purchase.
